<li>I took a quick look, and it seems that there are four parts to the test. Are those taken individually? Or all together? (And what are the sections?)
<ul><li>Will this accurately assess front-end developers? Or Backend/Sitebuilders.</li>
<li>What about specialists?</li>
</ul></li>
